# Live Search

Live Search is a simple web application that provides real-time search results as the user types in the search input field. Instead of waiting for the user to press the search button, results are automatically updated with every keystroke.

## 🚀 Features

* Real-time search functionality
* Instant results without page reload
* Fast and responsive user experience
* Clean and simple user interface

## ⚙️ How It Works

1. The user types a query into the search input.
2. A request is sent to fetch matching data.
3. The system processes the query and returns relevant results.
4. Results are displayed instantly without refreshing the page.

## 🛠 Technologies Used

* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript
* API / Backend (optional)

## 📌 Use Cases

This type of search functionality is commonly used in:

* E-commerce product search
* Blog or article search
* User directories
* Large data catalogs

## 🎯 Purpose

The main goal of this project is to improve search speed and user experience by providing dynamic, real-time search results.

